    "name": "Winter Witch Cold Sister",
    "type": "npc",
    "sections": [
        {
            "name": "Description",
            "html": "Nearly all of the White Witches ruling Irrisen are winter witches. This one represents a Cold Sister, a member of an organization devoted to hunting down anyone disloyal to the throne of Irrisen. Those the Cold Sisters find, they torture into compliance and devotion, or execute for their crimes against the queen."
        }
    ],
